CustomField.description: Calculates difference between dates excluding weekends.
CustomField.formula: (5 * ( FLOOR( ( DATEVALUE(Actual_Completion_Date__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8) ) / 7 ) ) + MIN( 5, MOD( DATEVALUE(Actual_Completion_Date__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8), 7 ) ) ) - (5 * ( FLOOR( ( DATEVALUE(Actual_Start_Date__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8) ) / 7 ) ) + MIN( 5, MOD( DATEVALUE(Actual_Start_Date__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8), 7 ) ) )
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Calculates difference between dates excluding weekends.
CustomField.label: Time to Complete 1
